eting.\n2.Forecasting & Trend Analysis: R’s time-series packages (like forecast) help businesses predict future sales, inventory needs, or stock market movements.\n3. Sentiment Analysis: Companies analyze social media feeds and customer reviews using R’s text mining tools to gauge brand perception.\n4.Risk Management: Financial institutions use R to build credit scoring models and perform stress testing to minimize loan defaults.\n5. Price Optimization: By analyzing demand elasticity, businesses use regression models in R to determine the best price points for ","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Data types**\n* Numeric\n* Integer\n* Character\n* Logical\n* Complex","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"a <- c(1,2,5.3,6,-2,4) \nb <- c(\"one\",\"two\",\"three\") \nc <- c(TRUE,TRUE,TRUE,FALSE,TRUE,FALSE) \nd <- c(4i, 3i)\ne<- c(2L)\nclass(a)\nclass(b)\nclass(c)\nclass(d)\nclass(e)\n","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.607883Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.609264Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.645490Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.643840Z"}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"'numeric'","text/markdown":"'numeric'","text/latex":"'numeric'","text/plain":"[1] \"numeric\""},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"'character'","text/markdown":"'character'","text/latex":"'character'","text/plain":"[1] \"character\""},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"'logical'","text/markdown":"'logical'","text/latex":"'logical'","text/plain":"[1] \"logical\""},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"'complex'","text/markdown":"'complex'","text/latex":"'complex'","text/plain":"[1] \"complex\""},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"'integer'","text/markdown":"'integer'","text/latex":"'integer'","text/plain":"[1] \"integer\""},"metadata":{}}],"execution_count":35},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**R-objects are data structures used to store and organize data.**\n* Vector: A sequence of data elements of the same basic type\n* Matrix: A 2D rectangular data set of the same type.\n* List: A collection of different types of R objects\n* Data Frame: A table-like structure where columns can have different data types\n* Factor: Used to categorize data and store it as levels\n* Array: Similar to matrices but can have more than two dimensions","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"vec <- c(1, 2, 3, 4)\nvec","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.647915Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.649255Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.666298Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.664537Z"}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"<style>\n.list-inline {list-style: none; margin:0; padding: 0}\n.list-inline>li {display: inline-block}\n.list-inline>li:not(:last-child)::after {content: \"\\00b7\"; padding: 0 .5ex}\n</style>\n<ol class=list-inline><li>1</li><li>2</li><li>3</li><li>4</li></ol>\n","text/markdown":"1. 1\n2. 2\n3. 3\n4. 4\n\n\n","text/latex":"\\begin{enumerate*}\n\\item 1\n\\item 2\n\\item 3\n\\item 4\n\\end{enumerate*}\n","text/plain":"[1] 1 2 3 4"},"metadata":{}}],"execution_count":36},{"cell_type":"code","source":"mat <- matrix(1:6, nrow=2, ncol=3)\nmat","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.668867Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.670258Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.690170Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-27T04:21:18.688375Z"}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"<table class=\"dataframe\">\n<caption>A matrix: 2 × 3 of type int</caption>\n<tbody>\n\t<tr><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>5</td></tr>\n\t<tr><td>2</td><td>4</td><td>6</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n","text/markdown":"\nA matrix: 2 × 3 of type int\n\n| 1 | 3 | 5 |\n| 2 | 4 | 